citeinfo.title: Boundaries:14(C)1, 14(H)1 and Native Allotments

descript.abstract: Data Type: Boundaries; Automation of the locations in the Copper River Basin of 14(c)1, 14(h)1 and native allotments. This dataset is part of the multilayered subsistence database compiled by UAA ISER for Copper River Native Association (Record #061)
